## Donation Support

This software is provided free of charge as open source. If you find this project 
useful and would like to support its continued development, we welcome donations.

### How to Donate

You can support the Clify project through:

- **GitHub Sponsors**: [Sponsor us on GitHub](https://github.com/sponsors/diptodesign)
- **Buy Me a Coffee**: [buymeacoffee.com/diptodesign100](https://buymeacoffee.com/diptodesign100)
- **PayPal**: [paypal.me/diptodesign98](https://paypal.me/diptodesign98)
- **Cryptocurrency**:
  - Bitcoin: `your-btc-address`
  - Ethereum: `your-eth-address`

### What Donations Support

Your donations help with:
- Server costs for synchronization features
- Continuous development and maintenance
- Testing equipment and services
- Supporting the open-source community

## Attribution

While not required, we appreciate attribution through:
- Linking back to our GitHub repository
- Mentioning Clify in your project's credits
- Sharing your experience with others

